					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Oh man, this is absolutely incredible. I love the beginning, it beautifully captures that slow, sinking feeling of dread that might come after seeing something that changes one's view of the world forever. It reminds me a bit of war of the worlds in the aspect that even though the end of humanity as we know it is approaching, daily life still continues on uneasily. The rest was amazing too, and I love the implication that the world has ended before without anybody knowing about it. Bravo, awesome piece</p> 
				 	]]>
