					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-220558#post-2470669</guid>
				<title>Short Film Adaptation</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-220558/document-recovered-from-the-marianas-trench#post-2470669</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 10 Mar 2016 21:54:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Doctor W White</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1859685</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm currently considering creating a short film adaptation of this tale, nothing solid yet, but I think it's worth giving it a shot. There are a few things I need to ask before I write up the screenplay and start a storyboard, though.</p> <p>-is this even allowed? If so, are there any restrictions?</p> <p>-Can someone please provide a complete list of SCPs or otherwise anomalous things described in the tale, so I can look into them in more detail?</p> <p>-Does anyone have any suggestions on how exactly I should portray this tale? Do tell if you do. I'll try and incorporate them if I can.</p> <p>-I may have to cut this down due to some constraints such as budgeting, time or that it's simply impractical for me to do with my available resources.</p> <p>I'm in a rush to get somewhere right now, so I'll add more if I think of them once I'm home.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
