				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-220558#post-2267770</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-220558/document-recovered-from-the-marianas-trench#post-2267770</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2015 04:46:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Agent MacLeod</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1922529</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is just&#8230; so <em>Foundation</em>. &quot;The world ends? Big deal. We have an Easy Button for that. We don't like pushing it, because that causes it's own trouble, but it's there when we need it. Why does it matter that good people died? We can copy-paste them a million times over.&quot;</p> <p>Like, the coldness the Foundation has for the end of the world, while simultaneously doing its best to save the world, is just so typical for them. It doesn't matter what happens, so long as normalcy is maintained and humanity stays safe.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
